name: BabyTracker
0:
”Alexa, tell BabyTracker my due date is August 24th.”
”Alexa, ask BabyTracker how big is my baby.”
”Alexa, open BabyTracker.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: baby tracker
des: BabyTracker allows you to monitor your baby's estimated size compared to everyday fruits and vegetables. Just provide your expected due date and ask BabyTracker "How big is my baby?!" everyweek for updates.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
